text: We've rounded up a few photos that serve as definitive proof that he was the swaggiest Commander-in-Chief of all time. From his tailored suits to laidback vacation attire, POTUS was definitely dressed to impress and had the swag to pull it all off. Take a look for yourself!
title: Definitive Proof That Barack Obama is the Swaggiest President Ever
